{
  "stem": "15694.7",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I-- later I was told probably they would think my father was too old for that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Little did they know that he was-- just by-- by one example, in this particular camp there was even once a football match arranged.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there, my father came on his own.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was rather proud because he showed the youngsters how to play, and how, and he was 48.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And well, the day came, the 31st of July, a recreation day.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we went outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And outside at the station, at the train, we met with the others, of the other sister camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They-- we were 200.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The others were 400. 600 mostly young, strong people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, if anybody knows about the history of these camps, the old, the weak, and the children were eliminated as soon as they reached camp, usually.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In-- especially in Auschwitz and the other camps of that type.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The young had a better chance.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Young, strong.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Slave work.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They needed slave-- slaves for the-- furthering the war effort.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not rounded up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We just asked to go to the train, and we went.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A number of people-- a number of people-- I'm not sure. 2, 4, 6, or 8 had escaped.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All that it is between the two factories, there were sort of like a traffic between horse-drawn carts being manufactured and being pushed from one way to another, and what we had to do I'm not quite sure.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But a group has taken such a number of carts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And while they were pushing out of our gate towards the other, the-- the guards wouldn't even watch because that's almost a daily thing to happen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only they did not go into the other camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They disappeared in the woods.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
